commit.message:
Do not add the Picture in picture window twice to the window list

The window is already added on the current workspace via
sendtoworkspace.
This created an issue in which the list had a dangling pointer when the
window was removed.
typo
Still handle the case for bar/panels to send window to other workspaces

Fix for picture in picture bug in Chrome-based browsers

Chrome based browser notify of window mapping on workspaces number
4294967295 which is erroneous, this fixes it an maps them properly.

Bug report from daechir

commit.message: On _NET_ACTIVE_WINDOW raise window to the top of the stack

Added support for _NET_WM_DESKTOP

2bwm now support _NET_WM_DESKTOP as defined by freedesktop, accepting
any source_indication
https://specifications.freedesktop.org/wm-spec/wm-spec-1.3.html#idm46175134505840

Commands relying on EWMH hints such as xdotool should work now, example:

xdotool getactivewindow set_desktop_for_window 3

Don't center pointer on click when not in sloppy mode

It's counter-intuitive to center the pointer on click in non-sloppy mode

Added sloppy-focus/click-to-focus toggle

As requested by @pyratebeard 2bwm now has the ability to switch between
a sloppy-focus mode and a click-to-focus mode by pressing mod4+s,
additional behavior can be added in the configuration (config.h) via the
sloppy_switch_cmd which will be triggered on the change.
